{"id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0003", "text": "像我的天職 早註定 只可將 別人伴侶", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 3, 3, 3, 9, 4, 2, 9, 9, 3, 2, 0, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zoeng6", "ngo5", "dik1", "tin1", "zik1", "zou2", "zyu3", "ding6", "zi2", "ho2", "zoeng1", "bit6", "jan4", "bun6", "leoi5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "像", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天職", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "早", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "註定", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "伴侶", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "司機", "artists": ["余文樂"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1060", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0004", "text": "護送往返 一起上路 無緣停下與你 看人間", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 5, 9, 3, 9, 2, 0, 0, 0, 2, 5, 5, 4, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["wu6", "sung3", "wong5", "faan2", "jat1", "hei2", "lou6", "mou4", "jyun4", "ting4", "haa6", "jyu5", "nei5", "hon3", "jan4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "護送", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "往返", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一起", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上路", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無緣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "停下", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "與", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "看", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "人間", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "司機", "artists": ["余文樂"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1060", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0005", "text": "隧道前 大路旁 鬧市間 火花 太短暫", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 0, 2, 2, 0, 2, 5, 9, 3, 4, 9, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi6", "dou6", "cin4", "daai6", "lou6", "pong4", "naau6", "si5", "fo2", "faa1", "taai3", "dyun2", "zaam6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "隧道", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "前", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "大", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "路旁", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "鬧市", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "間", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "火花", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "短暫", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "司機", "artists": ["余文樂"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1060", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0006", "text": "你約會 你喫飯 或買衫 但我 靠邊站", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 5, 4, 2, 2, 5, 3, 2, 5, 4, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "joek3", "nei5", "hek3", "faan6", "waak6", "maai5", "saam1", "daan6", "ngo5", "kaau3", "bin1", "zaam6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "約會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "喫飯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "或", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "買衫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "靠邊站", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "司機", "artists": ["余文樂"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1060", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0007", "text": "若你一伸手 總會在 多簡單 召來喚去", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 3, 3, 9, 9, 2, 3, 9, 3, 2, 0, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["joek6", "nei5", "jat1", "san1", "sau2", "zung2", "zoi6", "do1", "gaan2", "daan1", "ziu6", "loi4", "wun6", "heoi3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "伸手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "總會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "簡單", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "召來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "喚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "司機", "artists": ["余文樂"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1060", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0008", "text": "未到我揀 真的愛人 何曾同樣接你 上下班", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 5, 9, 3, 3, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 4, 5, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mei6", "dou3", "ngo5", "gaan2", "zan1", "dik1", "oi3", "jan4", "ho4", "cang4", "tung4", "joeng6", "zip3", "nei5", "haa6", "baan1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "未到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "揀", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "真的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "何曾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "同樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "接", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上下班", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "司機", "artists": ["余文樂"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1060", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0009", "text": "爲何還未看開 司機怎可以說不載", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 4, 3, 3, 3, 9, 9, 5, 4, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ho4", "waan4", "mei6", "hon3", "hoi1", "si1", "gei1", "zam2", "ho2", "ji5", "syut3", "bat1", "zoi2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "爲何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "看開", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "司機", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不載", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "司機", "artists": ["余文樂"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1060", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_5L2Z5paH5LmQ_MTA2MA_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
